OL,4,CIkea starts buy-back scheme with
OL,5,Cpromise to tackle waste
OL,6, Ikea has launched its long-awaited
OL,7, furniture buy-back and re-sale scheme,
OL,8, in an attempt to reduce the amount of
OL,9, products going to landfill.
OL,11,FThe move is part of the retail giant's
OL,12,Fsustainability drive to become "climate
OL,13,Fpositive" by 2030.
OL,15,FCustomers will get vouchers to spend
OL,16,Fin-store if items they no longer need
OL,17,Fare returned in good condition.
OL,19,FIkea admitted the scheme was a learning
OL,20,Fcurve, but decided to launch it after
OL,21,Fsuccessful trials in several cities.
